This paper deals with imitation learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. The paper discusses two popular methods for imitation learning, behavior cloning and GAIL, and proposes a new algorithm that combines the benefits of both. This work involves reinforcement learning, control theory, and robotics, which are all subfields of computer science. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.RO (Robotics), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
